            "title": "平安好醫生經調整淨利升逾161%   不派息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">平安好醫生(01833)公布，至2025年12月31日，經調整淨利潤4.14億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升161.25%。不派息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"平安好醫生官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01833_WEB_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"平安好醫生官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01833_WEB_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">平安好醫生官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">年內利潤3.78億元，按年升327.92%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入54.68億元，按年升13.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司商保協同業務收入32.96億元，按年增長11%，企業健管業務收入13.06億元，按年增長40.6% ；收入結構不斷優化，企業健管業務收入佔比達23.9%，同比提升4.6個百分點 ；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">毛利17.72億元，按年提升16.3%，高於收入增長幅度。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15784964-%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e5%a5%bd%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be161-%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01833-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-24 17:55:27",
